       \n                 \n                \t\n\t\n\u003ch5\u003e\n\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t        \t\t\t\t\n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/amazon-fire-max-11-review/\" title=\"Amazon Fire Max 11 review: Dude, where\u0026#39;s my app store?\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\n\t\t\tAmazon Fire Max 11 review: Dude, where\u0026#39;s my app store?\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\u003c/h5\u003e\n\n                                                    \n                \t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cp\u003eAmazon\u0026#39;s most expensive tablet yet is held back by a pitiful app experience\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\t\t\n\n                    \n\n\n                \n                \n                \n                \n\n                \n                \n                \n                \t\n\n\n                \n\n                \n                \n                \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eWhen it comes to battery life, this tablet performs pretty well, delivering up to 14 hours on a single charge. This tablet is also powered by Fire OS, which is a fork of Android and has its own Appstore. While you\u0026#39;ll find plenty of apps and games here, the selection won\u0026#39;t be as robust as what you\u0026#39;d find on the Google Play Store. \u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eFor the most part, this tablet is going to be great for someone that\u0026#39;s looking for something that\u0026#39;s simple, easy to use, and affordable. It excels with watching videos and surfing the web. It can also handle your productivity tasks too, but we recommend grabbing the keyboard case attachment to make things easier. \u003c/p\u003e    \u003cp\u003eOverall, the Fire Max 11 is a good product, and you\u0026#39;re getting excellent bang for your buck here. While Prime Day is just a couple of weeks away, we don\u0026#39;t think that it will be any cheaper. So just be sure to grab it while it\u0026#39;s on sale because this discount won\u0026#39;t last long.\u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\n    \n                \n        \n        \n\n\n        \n\n\n\n\n\n                                            \n\n\n\n\n        \n    \u003c/article\u003e\n\n    \n            \n        \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
